content.warning: Kōnke kōjerbal in ej jerbal n̄an juon ļapļo̧k in mālim ko ilo taļboon eo am̧, elōn̄ mālim ko rej lukkuun ļap aer kauwōtata, kōn menin jab bōktok ak kōm̧m̧ani ilo am jab lukkuun jeļā kōn jorrāān ko an m̧akūtkūt eo ak script eo. N̄e kwoj deļo̧n̄e men ko ilo "Kajin M̧akūtkūt eo" ak "Peij eo an M̧aket" bok eo ium̧win, men ko renaaj kōm̧m̧an m̧ōkaj āinwōt ko̧o̧t. Kwōn kōjparok.
